featured_reviews.review_id:
More than 550 years old This mosque is built in The region Of Hussain shah Sharqi(1458-1479) (the Last sultan of Sharqi Dynasty of Jaunpur Sultanate) who Also built the Shahi jama masjid of jaunpur & Makbara of Makhdoom jhaniya in ujjain.
It's A very simple mosuqe A minor memory of sharqi period The Main Gate is built later.
Qazi Nizammudin Hashmi Came to jaunpur from Arab & Become the Qazi of Machlishaher in 1417 Probably He built the mosque!
Sadly No rember Its history & Realise How old it's because it's not that magnificent.
